text: Julia Nowicka (born ) is a Polish female volleyball player. She is part of the Poland women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2015 FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship, 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League, and 2019 Montreux Volley Masters. On club level she played for BKS Profi Credit Bielsko Biala. ==References== ==External links== * CEV profile Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Polish women's volleyball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
